text: The AFL Grand Final is a football match (Australian Rules Football) held between the teams who won in the Preliminary Final the week before. This match normally takes place at the MCG on the last Saturday of September. The winner of this match is crowned as the best team of the season and gets the Premiership Cup. ==References== Category:Australian Football League Category:1898 establishments Category:Sport in Melbourne Category:1890s establishments in Australia Category:September events
